@startuml
title StatSync - System Context (C4 Level 1)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam rectangle {
  roundCorner 20
}

actor "Manager" as manager
actor "Player" as player

rectangle "StatSync\nFootball Analytics Platform" as system {
  rectangle "Mobile & Web Client\n(Expo / React Native)" as client
  rectangle "REST API & Business Logic\n(Django)" as api
  rectangle "Real-Time Updates\n(Node.js + Redis)" as realtime
  rectangle "Data Storage\n(PostgreSQL)" as db
}

manager --> client : Dashboards, event logging,\nvideo upload, analytics, chat
player --> client : Views own stats,\nteam chat

client --> api : HTTPS\nREST (JSON)
client --> realtime : WebSocket\nLive stats & chat
api --> db : SQL (ORM)
api --> realtime : Publish events

note right of system
  External users interact only
  with the client. All data
  flows through API or
  WebSocket services.
end note

@enduml
